trans-unit.source: Provides common functionality across communication protocols for generating classes for Web services.
trans-unit.target: 提供各种通信协议通用的功能，以用于为 Web 服务生成类。

trans-unit.source: The abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter> class and its concrete derived classes generate client proxy code or abstract server code according to a specified communication protocol.
trans-unit.target: 抽象<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter>类和具体派生的类生成客户端代理代码或根据指定的通信协议的抽象服务器代码。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter> provides common functionality regardless of the protocol.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter> 提供了常用的功能，不考虑的协议。

trans-unit.source: Within a given protocol, a concrete derived class generates a class for each supported binding defined in a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document.
trans-unit.target: 在给定的协议，具体派生的类生成每个受支持的绑定在 Web 服务描述语言 (WSDL) 文档中定义的类。

trans-unit.source: Typically, instead of directly invoking classes derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter>, a developer uses these classes indirectly through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter> class.
trans-unit.target: 通常情况下，而不是直接调用类派生自<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter>，开发人员可以使用这些类间接通过<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter>类。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets the abstract XML schemas used by the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 获取关联的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter" /> 实例所使用的抽象 XML 架构。

trans-unit.source: The abstract XML schemas used by the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter" /> instance
trans-unit.target: 关联的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImporter" /> 实例所使用的抽象 XML 架构。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeCommentStatementCollection" /> that specifies the collection of code comments to which each warning message is added.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeCommentStatementCollection" />，指定要将每个警告消息添加到的代码注释集合。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" /> that specifies the extensions or XML elements for which warnings should be generated if they are not handled.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection" />，指定如果未被处理则应为其生成警告的扩展或 XML 元素。

trans-unit.source: For each unhandled extension or XML element in the input extensions collection, turns on a <see cref="F:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings.RequiredExtensionsIgnored" /> or <see cref="F:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings.OptionalExtensionsIgnored" /> warning for each unhandled extension or XML element in the input extensions collection.
trans-unit.target: 对于输入扩展集合中的每个未处理的扩展或 XML 元素，打开 <see cref="F:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings.RequiredExtensionsIgnored" /> 或 <see cref="F:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionImportWarnings.OptionalExtensionsIgnored" /> 警告。

trans-unit.source: This method also adds the warning messages to a collection of code comments.
trans-unit.target: 此方法还将警告消息添加到代码注释的集合。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, initializes the generation of a binding class.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中重写时，初始化绑定类的生成。

trans-unit.source: The generated class.
trans-unit.target: 生成的类。

trans-unit.source: When generating a class for a given binding, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter> class calls the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.BeginClass%2A> method before generating methods that correspond to operations.
trans-unit.target: 生成为某个给定绑定的类时<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter>类调用<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.BeginClass%2A>之前生成的操作相对应的方法的方法。

trans-unit.target: 生成的方法。

trans-unit.source: When generating code, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter> class calls the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.GenerateMethod%2A> method for each binding class method that represents an operation.
trans-unit.target: 生成代码时，<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter>类调用<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.GenerateMethod%2A>为每个表示操作的绑定类方法的方法。

trans-unit.target: 获取协议导入程序当前正在处理，以在绑定类中生成方法的抽象操作的 Web 服务描述语言 (WSDL) 输入消息。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, determines whether a class can be generated for the current binding.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，确定是否可为当前绑定生成类。

trans-unit.source: True if the binding is supported; otherwise false.
trans-unit.target: True（如果支持绑定）；否则为 false。

trans-unit.source: When generating code, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter> class calls the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.IsBindingSupported%2A> method to determine whether to generate a class for the current binding, as represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.Binding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 生成代码时，<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter>类调用<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.IsBindingSupported%2A>方法来确定是否生成当前绑定的类所表示的<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.Binding%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow" /> enumeration value that represents a transmission pattern.
trans-unit.target: 表示传输模式的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow" /> 枚举值。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, determines whether the current operation's operation flow is supported.
trans-unit.target: 在派生类中重写时，确定当前操作的操作流是否受支持。

trans-unit.source: True if the current operation's operation flow is supported.
trans-unit.target: 如果当前操作的操作流受支持，则为 “True”。

trans-unit.source: When generating code, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter> class calls the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.IsOperationFlowSupported%2A> method to determine whether to generate a method for the current operation, as represented by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.Operation%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 生成代码时，<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter>类调用<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.IsOperationFlowSupported%2A>方法来确定是否生成当前操作，一种方法，由表示<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.Operation%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: This evaluation takes place for each operation in a binding for which a class is being generated.
trans-unit.target: 此计算都需要为其生成类的绑定中每个操作的位置。

trans-unit.source: If a `false` value is returned, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter> class calls its <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.UnsupportedOperationWarning%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 如果`false`返回值，<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter>类调用其<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ProtocolImporter.UnsupportedOperationWarning%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection.Flow%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 有关更多信息，请参见 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection.Flow%2A> 属性。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A> property is of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A> 属性为 <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection> 类型。
